name: BeeBase
description: $Bee, a BASE Memecoin, introduces a revolutionary mining mechanism set to innovate the game on Base Chain. A Quick Guide to BeeBase Welcome to the Buzz! You’re about to build the future BeeBase. As a pioneer in the land of data and innovation, you’re not just a keeper; you’re a commander of the CyberBee. Make sure you’ve read and signed below to secure your chance to be part of the early BeeBase buzz. 1. Bees Speak Bee Language Only:To chat with the bees, you’ll need to learn their lingo. Not sure where to start? Head over to Telegram; there’s a swarm waiting to welcome you. 2. Hard Work Pays Off:Bees are the embodiment of diligence, believing in the principle of reaping what you sow. If you’re looking for a free ride, it’s time for a change of heart. 3. Strength in Numbers:Bees thrive in colonies, leveraging the power of the group to build their hives. If going solo is your style, you might not be the right keeper for our BeeBase.
